          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="Element">Conjugate-Cam-FB</text> is now in the <text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Conjugate-Cam-FB">Conjugate-Cam dialog-box</link></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">In the </text><text styleclass="Element">Conjugate-Cam dialog-box</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> you will see:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName">Cam-Track </text><text styleclass="Body Text">: the names of the two(2)</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Element">2D-Cams</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> that are the </text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">Conjugate-Cams.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-indent">Cam-Flank Visible<text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> :</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> these will be </text><text styleclass="Parameter">Inner</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> or </text><text styleclass="Parameter">Outer Cam Flanks</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">When you open the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Forces-Configure-Power-Source" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">Configure-Power Source dialog-box</link><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">, the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Conjugate-Cam</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> is available to select as a </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Motor-Element</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
